name: Warung Sisin Tukad Blimbingsari
address: QG5G+9HV, Jl. Mawar, Blimbingsari, Kec. Melaya, Kabupaten Jembrana, Bali 82252, Indonesia
review 1: I love everything about this small warung. The architecture is an open air joglo style with natural wood. The location is perfect, next to a clear river. You can even hear the peaceful waterfall sound while eating here. Their best menu is fried duck with green & red chili sambal and fresh coconut. I hope there will be more menu in the future. Highly recommended!

name: Kebun Arya D
address: Blimbingsari, Melaya, Jembrana Regency, Bali 82252, Indonesia
